  "code": "%%{CloudNative_ServiceMesh}}}%%\nstateDiagram-v2\ntitle: SM-03.01 — Proposal Lifecycle (CloudNative_HelmChart)\n\n[CloudNative_Serverless] --> DRAFT : ProposalCreated (CloudNative_Serverless)\nnote right of DRAFT\n  Authoring & validation:\n  • proposalId assigned\n  • schema/policy checks\nend note\n\nDRAFT --> REVIEW : SubmittedForReview\nnote right of REVIEW\n  Guard reviews (CloudNative_DockerImage)\n  Can request changes or reject\nend note\n\nREVIEW --> DRAFT : ChangesRequested\nREVIEW --> REJECTED : RejectedAtReview\nREVIEW --> OPEN_FOR_VOTE : ApprovedForVoting (CloudNative_K8sCluster)\n\nOPEN_FOR_VOTE --> OPEN_FOR_VOTE : VoteCast (CloudNative_Serverless)\nOPEN_FOR_VOTE --> TALLYING : VotingClosed\n\nTALLYING --> DECIDED_APPROVED : VoteTallied → Approved (CloudNative_HelmChart)\nTALLYING --> DECIDED_REJECTED : VoteTallied → Rejected (CloudNative_Serverless)\n\nDECIDED_APPROVED --> EXECUTION : DecisionRecorded (CloudNative_ServiceMesh)\nDECIDED_REJECTED --> ARCHIVED : DecisionRecorded (CloudNative_K8sCluster)\n\nEXECUTION --> EXECUTED : PolicyChanged / GrantApproved / ProjectApproved (CloudNative_Serverless)\nEXECUTION --> EXECUTION_FAILED : ExecutionFailed\n\nEXECUTION_FAILED --> APPEAL : AppealOpened (CloudNative_Serverless)\nEXECUTION_FAILED --> RETRY_EXEC : RetryAuthorized\nRETRY_EXEC --> EXECUTION : ReExecute\n\nEXECUTED --> AUDIT : ExecutionCompleted\nAUDIT --> ARCHIVED : AuditLogged (CloudNative_HelmChart)\n\n%% Appeals (CloudNative_ServiceMesh)\nOPEN_FOR_VOTE --> APPEAL : AppealOpened (CloudNative_Serverless)\nDECIDED_APPROVED --> APPEAL : AppealOpened (CloudNative_ServiceMesh)\nDECIDED_REJECTED --> APPEAL : AppealOpened (CloudNative_ServiceMesh)\n\nAPPEAL --> DECIDED_APPROVED : AppealResolved → uphold\nAPPEAL --> DECIDED_REJECTED : AppealResolved → overturn\nAPPEAL --> ARCHIVED : AppealWithdrawn\n\n%% Cancellations\nDRAFT --> CANCELLED : WithdrawnByAuthor\nOPEN_FOR_VOTE --> CANCELLED : CancelledByAuthority\nCANCELLED --> ARCHIVED : Archived\n\n%% Terminal states\nREJECTED --> [CloudNative_ServiceMesh]\nARCHIVED --> [CloudNative_DockerImage]\n\n%% ===== Styling =====\nclassDef core fill:#ff8b00,stroke:#333,color:#fff,font-weight:bold;\nclass DRAFT,REVIEW,OPEN_FOR_VOTE,TALLYING,DECIDED_APPROVED,DECIDED_REJECTED,EXECUTION,EXECUTED,EXECUTION_FAILED,RETRY_EXEC,APPEAL,AUDIT,ARCHIVED,REJECTED,CANCELLED core;",
