  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为提案生命周期设计一个状态图，覆盖从创建到归档的完整流程。这个系统要跑在云原生架构上，特别是HelmChart部署的环境。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_HelmChart",
        "proposal lifecycle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，HelmChart作为部署载体。那提案的起点是什么状态？我假设是DRAFT草稿态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DRAFT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，DRAFT是起点。提案通过Serverless函数触发创建，需要记录proposalId，还要做schema和policy校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DRAFT",
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "proposalId",
        "schema/policy checks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画了DRAFT状态，右侧加了注释说明authoring和validation环节。接下来提交后进入什么状态？",
